querySubject.name: GDYR_CAL
querySubject.description: View containing various dates and date calculations for the data warehouse.

queryItem.name: DAY_DATE
queryItem.description: Sequential Date in the Calendar Table starting with 1/1/1990 and ending with 12/31/2050.

queryItem.name: DAY_OF_WEEK
queryItem.description: Sequential day of the week, calculated from DAY_DATE and using Sunday as Day 1, Mon day2, etc. e.g. 1990-01-01 is a Monday and therefore calculated as DAY_OF_WK = 2.

queryItem.name: DAY_OF_WEEK_NAME_ABBREV
queryItem.description: Month abbreviation based on DAY_DATE - Values: Mon, Tue, Wed, Thu, Fri, Sat, Sun.

queryItem.name: DAY_OF_WEEK_NAME_DESC
queryItem.description: Month Name based on DAY_DATE - Values: Monday, Tuesday, etc.

queryItem.name: WEEKDAY_IN_MONTH_OCCURENCE
queryItem.description: The nth time the weekday occurs in the month

queryItem.name: DAY_OF_MONTH
queryItem.description: Sequential Numeric day of Month, 1 to 31 depending on month.

queryItem.name: DAY_OF_QTR
queryItem.description: Sequential, Numeric Day of the financial Quarter, based on DAY_DATE, and re-initiated to 1 on the first day of the subsequent quarter.

queryItem.name: DAY_OF_YEAR
queryItem.description: Sequential, Numeric day of the year, starting with day 1 and ending with 365 or 366 - based on DAY_DATE.

queryItem.name: CAL_LAST_DAY_MO_IND
queryItem.description: Values Y or N. Value is N except on the last day of a given month. For the last day of a given month, the value is "Y".

queryItem.name: CAL_LAST_DAY_YR_IND
queryItem.description: Values Y or N. Value is N except on the last day of a given year. On the last day of the year, the value will be "Y".

queryItem.name: CAL_WK
queryItem.description: CAL_WK is Numeric Value of the DAY_DATE week (Values 1 through 52). CAL_WK 1 begins with the first Sunday in a new year, etc.

queryItem.name: CAL_MTH
queryItem.description: CAL_MTH is Numeric Value of the DAY_DATE month. Jan will be 1, Feb will be 2, Dec will be 12.

queryItem.name: CAL_YR
queryItem.description: CAL_YR is Numeric Value of the DAY_DATE Year. The equivalent of extract(year from day_date).

queryItem.name: MNTH
queryItem.description: MNTH is Alphanumeric abbreviation of DAY_DATE Month and Year. e.g. "JAN 1990".

queryItem.name: MNTH_DESCR
queryItem.description: MNTH_DESCR is Alphanumeric expression of DAY_DATE Month and Year. e.g. "January 1990".

queryItem.name: MNTH_SEQ
queryItem.description: MNTH_SEQ is Alphanumeric sequence of DAY_DATE Month and Year providing the ASCII sequence. e.g. "1990-01" is January of 1990.

queryItem.name: MNTH_NAME_ABBREV
queryItem.description: Abbreviation of the month in DAY_DATE. e.g. JAN, FEB, MAR, etc.

queryItem.name: MNTH_NAME
queryItem.description: The month in DAY_DATE. January, February, March, etc.

queryItem.name: MONTH_OF_QUARTER
queryItem.description: Numerical sequence of the Financial Quarter Month for the date in DAY_DATE. e.g. Jan = 1, Feb = 2, Mar = 3, Apr = 1, etc.

queryItem.name: LAST_SHIP_DAY_MO_IND
queryItem.description: Identifies the last shipping day of the month.

queryItem.name: QTR_NO
queryItem.description: Alphanumeric identifier of the Financial Quarter for DAY_DATE.

queryItem.name: QUARTER_OF_YEAR
queryItem.description: Numeric identifier for the Financial Quarter of the date in DAY_DATE. Values 1 to 4.

queryItem.name: QTR_DESCR
queryItem.description: Alphanumeric description of the Financial Quarter for DAY_DATE. e.g. First Quarter 1990.

queryItem.name: QTR_SEQ
queryItem.description: Alphanumeric sequence of the QTR for day date e.g. 1990 QTR 1.

queryItem.name: SHIP_DAY_OF_MO
queryItem.description: Numeric sequence of of day in month on which shipments occur.

queryItem.name: WEEK_OF_MONTH
queryItem.description: Numeric sequence of week of month in DAY_DATE. Values 0 - 5, the nth full week of month, first partial week is 0.

queryItem.name: WEEK_OF_YEAR
queryItem.description: Numeric sequence of week of year in DAY_DATE. Values 0 - 53, the nth full week of year, first partial week is 0.

queryItem.name: WEEKDAY_OF_MONTH
queryItem.description: Values 1 - 5, the nth occurrence of the weekday in the month. e.g. The third Tuesday of the month will have a value of 3.

queryItem.name: FIFTH_WRK_DY_IND
queryItem.description: Fifth Workday of the Month.

queryItem.name: TWENTIETH_WRK_DY_IND
queryItem.description: Twentieth Workday of the Month.

queryItem.name: MTH_WRK_DYS
queryItem.description: Number of workdays for the month in DAY_DATE.

queryItem.name: PERIOD_SK
queryItem.description: Ship to level key to THE P_RBNATP.PERIOD Table corresponding to DAY_DATE.

queryItem.name: CALENDAR_DATE
queryItem.description: The same as DAY_DATE. Included for backwards compatibility.

queryItem.name: DAY_OF_WEEK_ISO
queryItem.description: Numeric sequence of day of week of in DAY_DATE using MONDAY as the first day of the week.

queryItem.name: MONTH_OF_YEAR
queryItem.description: Numeric sequence representing the Month of the Year. e.g January = 1.

queryItem.name: TOT_CAL_MTHS
queryItem.description: The number of months that have passed for a given date. Hypothetical Year 0 is used as the base. The current month is included in the calculation. e.g. Feb from the beginning of the calendar would be (12*0) +2 = 2. Jan 1990 would be 1990*12 +1 = 23881.

queryItem.name: MTHS_AGO
queryItem.description: How many MONTHS have passed between the current date and DAY_DATE.

queryItem.name: QTRS_AGO
queryItem.description: How many FINANCIAL QUARTERS have passed between the current quarter and the quarter related to a given DAY_DATE.

queryItem.name: YRS_AGO
queryItem.description: How many YEARS have passed between the current date and DAY_DATE.

queryItem.name: TOT_CURR_MTHS
queryItem.description: How many MONTHS have passed between the current date and the beginning of the calendar. i.e. how many months have transpired for the current year and month.

querySubject.name: Facility
querySubject.description: Contains Facilty Type, Id, Description, & Location
querySubject.screenTip: Contains Facilty Type, Id, Description, & Location

modelQuery.sql: select Facility.Company_Code as Company_Code, Facility.Company_Name as Company_Name, Facility.Facility_Type_Id as Facility_Type_Id, Facility.Facility_Id as Facility_Id, Facility.Facility_Desc as Facility_Desc, Facility.Country_Id as Country_Id, Facility.City_Id as City_Id, Facility.EU_USAGE_CD as EU_USAGE_CD, Facility.FACILITY_CAT_ID as FACILITY_CAT_ID, Facility.INT_CUST_ID as INT_CUST_ID, Facility.PURCH_ORG_ID as PURCH_ORG_ID, Facility.SALES_ORG_CD as SALES_ORG_CD, Facility.TERR_ID as TERR_ID, Facility.VAL_AREA_ID as VAL_AREA_ID, Facility.VENDOR_CUST_ID as VENDOR_CUST_ID, Facility.ACTIV_REQ_PLAN_IND as ACTIV_REQ_PLAN_IND, Facility.FACILITY_ACTIV_IND as FACILITY_ACTIV_IND, Facility.SPLC_CD as SPLC_CD, Facility.SRC_LOC_CD as SRC_LOC_CD, Facility.XTND_NAME as XTND_NAME from (select NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID as Facility_Id, XMIN(NAT_CO_EN_CURR.CO_CD for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as Company_Code, XMIN(NAT_CO_EN_CURR.NAME for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as Company_Name, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_TYPE_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as Facility_Type_Id, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_NAME for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as Facility_Desc, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.CNTRY_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as Country_Id, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.CITY_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as City_Id, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.EU_USAGE_CD for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as EU_USAGE_CD, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_CAT_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as FACILITY_CAT_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.INT_CUST_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as INT_CUST_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.PURCH_ORG_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as PURCH_ORG_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.SALES_ORG_CD for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as SALES_ORG_CD, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.TERR_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as TERR_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.VAL_AREA_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as VAL_AREA_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.VENDOR_CUST_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as VENDOR_CUST_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.ACTIV_REQ_PLAN_IND for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as ACTIV_REQ_PLAN_IND, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ACTIV_IND for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as FACILITY_ACTIV_IND, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.SPLC_CD for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as SPLC_CD, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.SRC_LOC_CD for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as SRC_LOC_CD, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.XTND_NAME for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as XTND_NAME from [GDYR_BI_VWS].NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR, [GDYR_BI_VWS].NAT_CO_EN_CURR NAT_CO_EN_CURR, [GDYR_BI_VWS].NAT_SALES_ORG_EN_CURR NAT_SALES_ORG_EN_CURR1 where (NAT_SALES_ORG_EN_CURR1.SALES_ORG_CD = NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.SALES_ORG_CD) and (NAT_CO_EN_CURR.CO_CD = NAT_SALES_ORG_EN_CURR1.CO_CD) group by NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) Facility

modelQuery.sql: select Facility.Company_Code as Company_Code, Facility.Company_Name as Company_Name, Facility.Facility_Type_Id as Facility_Type_Id, Facility.Facility_Id as Facility_Id, Facility.Facility_Desc as Facility_Desc, Facility.Country_Id as Country_Id, Facility.City_Id as City_Id, Facility.EU_USAGE_CD as EU_USAGE_CD, Facility.FACILITY_CAT_ID as FACILITY_CAT_ID, Facility.INT_CUST_ID as INT_CUST_ID, Facility.PURCH_ORG_ID as PURCH_ORG_ID, Facility.SALES_ORG_CD as SALES_ORG_CD, Facility.TERR_ID as TERR_ID, Facility.VAL_AREA_ID as VAL_AREA_ID, Facility.VENDOR_CUST_ID as VENDOR_CUST_ID, Facility.ACTIV_REQ_PLAN_IND as ACTIV_REQ_PLAN_IND, Facility.FACILITY_ACTIV_IND as FACILITY_ACTIV_IND, Facility.SPLC_CD as SPLC_CD, Facility.SRC_LOC_CD as SRC_LOC_CD, Facility.XTND_NAME as XTND_NAME from (select NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID as Facility_Id, XMIN(NAT_CO_EN_CURR.CO_CD for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as Company_Code, XMIN(NAT_CO_EN_CURR.NAME for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as Company_Name, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_TYPE_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as Facility_Type_Id, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_NAME for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as Facility_Desc, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.CNTRY_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as Country_Id, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.CITY_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as City_Id, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.EU_USAGE_CD for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as EU_USAGE_CD, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_CAT_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as FACILITY_CAT_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.INT_CUST_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as INT_CUST_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.PURCH_ORG_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as PURCH_ORG_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.SALES_ORG_CD for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as SALES_ORG_CD, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.TERR_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as TERR_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.VAL_AREA_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as VAL_AREA_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.VENDOR_CUST_ID for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as VENDOR_CUST_ID, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.ACTIV_REQ_PLAN_IND for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as ACTIV_REQ_PLAN_IND, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ACTIV_IND for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as FACILITY_ACTIV_IND, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.SPLC_CD for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as SPLC_CD, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.SRC_LOC_CD for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as SRC_LOC_CD, XMIN(NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.XTND_NAME for NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) as XTND_NAME from [GDYR_BI_VWS].NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR, [GDYR_BI_VWS].NAT_CO_EN_CURR NAT_CO_EN_CURR, [GDYR_BI_VWS].NAT_SALES_ORG_EN_CURR NAT_SALES_ORG_EN_CURR1 where (NAT_SALES_ORG_EN_CURR1.SALES_ORG_CD = NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.SALES_ORG_CD) and (NAT_CO_EN_CURR.CO_CD = NAT_SALES_ORG_EN_CURR1.CO_CD) group by NAT_FACILITY_EN_CURR.FACILITY_ID ) Facility

filter.expression: [Business Layer].[Inventory].[Inventory Date] between #$[Start Date]{'Current Year'}# and #$[End Date]{'Current Year'}#

filter.name: Inventory Date Prior Year
filter.screenTip: Prior Year filters for all for the previous year records.
filter.expression: [Business Layer].[Inventory].[Inventory Date] between #$[Start Date]{'Prior Year'}# and #$[End Date]{'Prior Year'}#

filter.name: Inventory Date Prior YTD
filter.screenTip: Prior YTD returns the prior year up to the yesterday's date prior year. For example, if Current Day is 6/27/2011 this will return records from 1/1/2010 to 6/26/2010. This is useful for Year over Year comparisons.
filter.expression: [Business Layer].[Inventory].[Inventory Date] between #$[Start Date]{'Prior YTD'}# and #$[End Date]{'Prior YTD'}#

filter.name: Inventory Date Current Year through Prior Month
filter.screenTip: Current Year through Prior Month returns the entire current year up to the last day of the prior month. For example, if Current Day is 6/27/2011 this will return records from 1/1/2011 to 5/31/2011.
filter.expression: [Business Layer].[Inventory].[Inventory Date] between #$[Start Date]{'Current Year'}# and #$[End Date]{'Prior Month'}#

filter.name: Inventory Date Prior Year through Prior Month Last Year
filter.screenTip: Prior Year through Prior Month Last Year returns the prior year up to the last day of the prior month last year. For example, if Current Day is 6/27/2011 this will return records from 1/1/2010 to 5/31/2010.
filter.expression: [Business Layer].[Inventory].[Inventory Date] between #$[Start Date]{'Prior Year'}# and #$[End Date]{'Prior Month Last Year'}#
